1
00:01:06,719 --> 00:01:07,760
Best two out of three.

2
00:01:09,719 --> 00:01:11,920
When we disagreed with each other,

3
00:01:12,879 --> 00:01:14,840
we would fight to solve the problem.

4
00:01:16,079 --> 00:01:17,040
Best two out of three.

5
00:01:17,359 --> 00:01:18,319
The winner has the final say.

6
00:01:19,079 --> 00:01:20,480
I won in the end anyway.

7
00:01:21,079 --> 00:01:21,959
Then I'll make a decision.

8
00:01:23,599 --> 00:01:25,079
Sister, you should stay here.

9
00:01:30,959 --> 00:01:31,680
A Che

10
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:34,319
You have to keep your promise

11
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,760
to ensure our safety.

12
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:36,400
Okay.

13
00:01:52,519 --> 00:01:55,280
Humans eat moon cakes on the Mid-Autumn Festival.

14
00:01:56,719 --> 00:01:59,159
You eat small cakes on the Shuomu Festival.

15
00:01:59,719 --> 00:02:00,760
It's cute.

16
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:04,599
We are affected by the tidal force.

17
00:02:05,359 --> 00:02:06,799
We will go wild on the night of the full moon.

18
00:02:07,359 --> 00:02:08,280
Only on the night of the new moon

19
00:02:08,879 --> 00:02:10,479
can we calm down and be sensible.

20
00:02:11,639 --> 00:02:14,080
The first high priest set up the Shuomu Festival

21
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,719
to tell us that

22
00:02:16,719 --> 00:02:18,840
wisdom and calmness are to be advocated.

23
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:20,719
Violence

24
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,680
is not the best way.

25
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:27,039
Calm and rational.

26
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:36,400
The kind that can remain calm in any situation.

27
00:02:41,719 --> 00:02:43,319
It's not the Shuomu Festival yet.

28
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:46,560
I can't be completely calm and rational.

29
00:03:00,639 --> 00:03:01,280
Uncle Wang

30
00:03:01,919 --> 00:03:03,400
It's rare to see you in such a good mood.

31
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:04,599
Of course.

32
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:07,560
I usually live with a bunch of wolves

33
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,439
and have to serve my brother.

34
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,520
Now,

35
00:03:11,719 --> 00:03:12,479
I finally look forward to

36
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:15,080
the day when everyone can sit together

37
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,759
singing and dancing together.

38
00:03:18,199 --> 00:03:18,719
Wang,

39
00:03:19,439 --> 00:03:20,560
am I usually that fierce?

40
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,960
When have I ever punished you?

41
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,759
With Miss Jiang by your side,

42
00:03:25,879 --> 00:03:26,879
of course you

43
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:28,560
have to be a bit more gentlemanly.

44
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:34,280
He used to

45
00:03:34,639 --> 00:03:35,879
fight with Zhang San and Li Si

46
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,439
every day outside.

47
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:38,639
As for me,

48
00:03:39,039 --> 00:03:40,520
I had to repair the house and the garden.

49
00:03:41,879 --> 00:03:43,039
I was so tired.

50
00:03:45,599 --> 00:03:46,919
You're asking for a beating.

51
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:49,439
Be nice to me.

52
00:04:13,439 --> 00:04:15,039
What a terrible story.

53
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:28,000
If you don't keep an eye on Qin Yaxin,

54
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,079
and she gets into trouble,

55
00:04:29,319 --> 00:04:30,319
you'll be responsible.

56
00:04:31,399 --> 00:04:32,879
She's already asleep.

57
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:34,680
A Che

58
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,959
You never trust humans,

59
00:04:38,639 --> 00:04:39,959
but you're not wary of her.

60
00:04:42,199 --> 00:04:42,839
Anyway,

61
00:04:42,879 --> 00:04:44,720
I've been a hunter for hundreds of years.

62
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,759
I have a sense of danger.

63
00:04:47,279 --> 00:04:48,399
I can guarantee that

64
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,680
Qin Yaxin

65
00:04:50,199 --> 00:04:52,079
is absolutely not a bad person.

66
00:04:55,639 --> 00:04:57,079
Are you going to take her to the Shuomu Festival

67
00:04:57,959 --> 00:04:59,199
tomorrow?

68
00:05:00,519 --> 00:05:01,000
Is that okay?

69
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,079
If you go on like this,

70
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,480
sooner or later, you'll let her know

71
00:05:07,639 --> 00:05:08,680
all your secrets.

72
00:05:14,959 --> 00:05:16,160
I'm afraid to stimulate her

73
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:17,839
and run away from me.

74
00:05:18,759 --> 00:05:20,279
With her temper,

75
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,439
I think I'd better keep it from her.

76
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:28,040
Please don't guess girls' hearts at will.

77
00:05:28,879 --> 00:05:30,120
Speak out your mind.

78
00:05:32,399 --> 00:05:33,680
You know a lot.

79
00:05:34,959 --> 00:05:36,319
Actually, I don't know much.

80
00:05:37,639 --> 00:05:39,160
I just give you all I know.

81
00:05:42,079 --> 00:05:42,680
Brother

82
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:48,879
Actually, sometimes I

83
00:05:50,319 --> 00:05:51,279
miss mom and dad.

84
00:05:58,879 --> 00:06:00,439
Our ancestors taught us to be peaceful.

85
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:03,160
But when the wolves face the Shuoyue,

86
00:06:03,639 --> 00:06:05,439
they are the weakest in strength and will.

87
00:06:06,519 --> 00:06:07,519
Those imperial bodyguards

88
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:09,199
put chains on them

89
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,680
and locked them up in cages.

90
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,920
They were paraded like prisoners.

91
00:06:13,199 --> 00:06:14,439
Do you know how much I hate them?

92
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,759
There's a saying among humans.

93
00:06:21,879 --> 00:06:22,759
Those who are not of our kind

94
00:06:23,879 --> 00:06:24,959
must have different hearts.

95
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,720
We have to guard against betrayal from friends

96
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:29,639
and plunder from outsiders.

97
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:31,639
This is the fear of the weak.

98
00:06:32,879 --> 00:06:34,639
The real strong man should be confident,

99
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:36,720
composed,

100
00:06:37,879 --> 00:06:39,639
and fearless of any future obstacles.

101
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:46,199
You've grown a lot.

102
00:06:49,879 --> 00:06:51,079
I'll invite Qin Yaxin right now.

103
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,240
Go.

104
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:58,360
Cherish the calm before the storm.

105
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:33,240
It's so late.

106
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:34,480
Why are you here?

107
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,120
I should ask you.

108
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:38,040
There's no one around to watch over you at night.

109
00:07:38,519 --> 00:07:40,120
What if something happened to you?

110
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:42,879
There are only these animals around.

111
00:07:43,399 --> 00:07:44,720
Could they possibly hurt me?

112
00:07:45,879 --> 00:07:46,800
You're overreacting.

113
00:07:48,399 --> 00:07:49,800
So, what are you doing here at this hour?

114
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,639
I'm here to invite you

115
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,920
to our Shuomuyue Festival.

116
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,639
Shuomuyue Festival?

117
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:01,560
I've never heard of such a festival.

118
00:08:02,399 --> 00:08:03,240
Is it a lively celebration?

119
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,480
During this festival,

120
00:08:05,079 --> 00:08:06,279
we gather together,

121
00:08:06,399 --> 00:08:07,000
sing,

122
00:08:07,399 --> 00:08:07,959
dance,

123
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,360
and

124
00:08:13,759 --> 00:08:15,000
confess to someone we like.

125
00:08:17,319 --> 00:08:18,480
That's definitely something to see.

126
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:19,360
I'll go.

127
00:08:23,959 --> 00:08:24,480
Is it pretty?

128
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,519
It looks familiar.

129
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:32,159
Ancestors learned some customs from humans,

130
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:34,919
like exorcism and hanging sachets.

131
00:08:36,559 --> 00:08:38,200
Your knowledge is all mixed up.

132
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,799
Is there really a ball tomorrow?

133
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:45,279
So,

134
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,360
if there is a ball,

135
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,240
will you be my partner?

136
00:08:51,039 --> 00:08:52,679
Just singing and dancing,

137
00:08:53,039 --> 00:08:54,440
or is there something else?

138
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,440
We stand in the center of the altar,

139
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:01,279
receiving blessings from everyone.

140
00:09:02,399 --> 00:09:04,840
Isn't that a bit too grand?

141
00:09:05,799 --> 00:09:07,159
I'd rather just be an audience.

142
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:10,200
It's okay.

143
00:09:11,639 --> 00:09:12,720
I won't force you.

144
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:33,679
It seems like you're really about to recover.

145
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,559
Isn't that good?

146
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,519
You can be free.

147
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:43,919
Even you think

148
00:09:45,399 --> 00:09:46,279
I should leave?

149
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:48,600
Unless

150
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,120
you don't want to leave the brand

151
00:09:50,759 --> 00:09:52,480
and stay here forever

152
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:54,600
as his contracted bride.

153
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,000
How is that possible?

154
00:09:56,799 --> 00:09:58,200
I will soon grow old,

155
00:09:58,840 --> 00:10:00,360
with grey hair and wrinkles.

156
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,759
I can't be like Old Wang,

157
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,240
be his mother,

158
00:10:04,519 --> 00:10:05,600
and then his grandmother.

159
00:10:07,919 --> 00:10:09,000
This situation

160
00:10:09,639 --> 00:10:11,120
reminds me of an ancient poem.

161
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,240
A beauty cherishes her youth,

162
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:16,559
afraid it will fade away.

163
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:19,000
At dusk, she leaves the hall,

164
00:10:19,759 --> 00:10:21,279
and bows to the new moon.

165
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:25,399
A woman prays to the new moon for eternal youth.

166
00:10:26,279 --> 00:10:28,200
But she doesn't know that aging is

167
00:10:29,679 --> 00:10:30,879
already a blessing.

168
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:34,120
I'm sorry.

169
00:10:35,159 --> 00:10:36,840
I shouldn't have told you these.

170
00:10:43,799 --> 00:10:44,279
Brother

171
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:47,080
Everything is ready for tomorrow.

172
00:10:47,879 --> 00:10:48,360
Thank you.

173
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:51,440
Now everyone can celebrate the festival happily

174
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:54,039
without being frightened

175
00:10:54,559 --> 00:10:55,480
of losing their power.

176
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,799
It all depends on your protection

177
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,039
for so many years.

178
00:10:59,679 --> 00:11:00,799
Although I'm not from the clan,

179
00:11:01,919 --> 00:11:03,200
I'm deeply moved

180
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,519
from the bottom of my heart.

181
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:08,039
Flattery.

182
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:09,919
What do you want to say?

183
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:14,159
Although I don't have much family

184
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:15,039
to reunite with,

185
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:15,919
I also

186
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,279
want to take a vacation

187
00:11:17,519 --> 00:11:18,200
and just relax for a day.

188
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:20,759
Just one day.

189
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:23,279
Go.

190
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:31,279
I'll give you seven days off

191
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:32,440
with pay.

192
00:11:54,159 --> 00:11:54,559
Bro.

193
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,159
Stop drinking.

194
00:11:57,039 --> 00:11:58,120
Stop drinking.

195
00:11:58,480 --> 00:11:59,360
Leave me alone.

196
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,039
Why are you here?

197
00:12:18,519 --> 00:12:19,000
Hello.

198
00:12:19,759 --> 00:12:20,679
Where are you?

199
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:23,720
It's none of your business.

200
00:12:24,639 --> 00:12:25,440
You're drunk.

201
00:12:26,519 --> 00:12:27,879
You really disappointed me.

202
00:12:28,679 --> 00:12:30,799
You didn't do anything you promised me.

203
00:12:31,399 --> 00:12:32,200
The order was ruined.

204
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:33,440
Qin Yeren was exposed.

205
00:12:33,679 --> 00:12:35,440
and the girl you were supposed to keep an eye on is also lost.

206
00:12:35,919 --> 00:12:37,639
And now you're so self-destructive.

207
00:12:38,279 --> 00:12:39,679
How can you be like the son of the Xie family?

208
00:12:41,799 --> 00:12:42,440
Son?

209
00:12:45,799 --> 00:12:47,399
Do you treat me as your son

210
00:12:48,399 --> 00:12:50,080
or as your pawn?

211
00:12:50,159 --> 00:12:51,600
You know it in your heart.

212
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:57,840
I don't want to get involved

213
00:12:58,159 --> 00:13:00,080
in those dirty things of the group from beginning to end.

214
00:13:02,559 --> 00:13:03,600
Those health products

215
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:06,840
can make the Xie family enjoy wealth and honor,

216
00:13:07,279 --> 00:13:08,919
but can they save my sister's life?

217
00:13:10,799 --> 00:13:13,279
I could have attended the best medical school.

218
00:13:14,639 --> 00:13:15,559
It was you

219
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:19,519
who deceived me with these illusions.

220
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:20,240
Shut up!

221
00:13:20,799 --> 00:13:22,519
If others hear these crazy words,

222
00:13:22,559 --> 00:13:24,519
you'll put me in prison too, right?

223
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:26,120
Come on.

224
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:45,399
Dad.
